<TEXT>  JULY 21: Welcome to <LOCATION>Barcelona</LOCATION>, where <LOCATION>Columbus</LOCATION> returned in triumph to meet
<LOCATION>Ferdinand</LOCATION> and <PERSON>Isabella</PERSON> after his <DATE>1492</DATE> voyage. It's the site of the <DATE>1992</DATE>
Olympics, site of some fine Middle Ages buildings -- and the site of humongous
traffic jams.; <DATE>JULY 28</DATE>: Where's the body? Everybody has a theory where
<LOCATION>Columbus</LOCATION> is stashed, but nobody's sure. Is it <LOCATION>Seville</LOCATION> (site of the <DATE>1992</DATE> Expo)
or is he really buried under a cafe in <LOCATION>Valladolid</LOCATION>?  </TEXT>
